	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Sep 12th 7:58 AM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.90]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just a brief note, this isn't Magic *Bane* damage it's Magic Damage, in the same as some weapons have cold, disease, fire or poison damage modifiers. Basically the opponent makes a Save vs Magic every hit and if unsuccessful the weapon is treated as 44 damage and not 40 damage.<br>This damage applies to all mobs, whereas bane damage only applies to one specific type (Lizardmen, Summoned, Undead etc) and, afaik, is an unresistable bonus.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
